Page_0:
"The guy in the orange working suit who calls himself \"Friend Turbine\" brought in the last parts of the wood chipper. The thing seems to be working all right, though I still don't understand how it can tell apart what you throw into it.

I overheard Turbine mumbling to himself about the Builder when he was working. I asked him if he'd been a Hammerite once, and he answered that we were at the dawn of a new age. Whatever that means."
